snippet.textDisplay:
The song did not get justice from this singer. She has all the skills, but her 'loy' and 'tal' was too fast to sink the lyrics in. The song needs a style, drama which is urged by the lyrics and its origin. 
Also the sudden western tunes during antora was not necessary, it did not even blend. As I said grammatically it is fine, but it failed to touch the heart.
